---
export const prerender = false;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Terms of Use - emdashcms.org';
const description = 'Terms of use for the emdashcms.org community marketplace.';
const lastUpdated = '2026-04-06';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="page pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-16">
    <div class="page-narrow">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-ink mb-4" style="font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Terms of Use
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-soft">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-body text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-6 max-w-prose text-base">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">1. About emdashcms.org</h2>
          <p>
            emdashcms.org is an independent, community-operated marketplace for plugins and themes that target
            <a href="https://emdashcms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ink underline hover:opacity-80">EmDash CMS</a>.
            It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or operated by the EmDash CMS project or Cloudflare. The
            marketplace is open-source and runs on Cloudflare's free tier. The source code is available at
            <a href="https://github.com/chrisjohnleah/emdashcms-org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ink underline hover:opacity-80">github.com/chrisjohnleah/emdashcms-org</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">2. Acceptance of terms</h2>
          <p>
            By using this site — browsing, installing plugins, uploading a bundle, reporting a problem — you agree
            to these terms and to our
            <a href="/code-of-conduct" class="text-ink underline hover:opacity-80">Code of Conduct</a>.
            If you don't agree, please don't use the marketplace.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">3. Ownership of your content</h2>
          <p>
            You retain full ownership of any plugin, theme, bundle, review, or other content you upload. By
            publishing a plugin or theme here, you grant emdashcms.org a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free
            licence to store, distribute, and display your content as part of the marketplace's normal operation.
            This licence ends when you ask us to remove the content (or when it's removed under our review policy).
          </p>
          <p>
            You must have the right to license every file you upload. If you include third-party code, it must be
            under a compatible open-source licence and that licence must be respected in your bundle.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">4. Acceptable use</h2>
          <p>
            You agree not to upload plugins or themes that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-ink-muted">
            <li>Contain malicious code, backdoors, cryptomining, or data exfiltration logic.</li>
            <li>Infringe on copyrights, trademarks, or other intellectual property rights.</li>
            <li>Violate applicable laws or regulations.</li>
            <li>Impersonate another person, organisation, or project.</li>
            <li>Are designed to bypass our static scanner or other review gates.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Our full review policy — including the static scanner's ruleset in plain English — is published at
            <a href="/docs/security" class="text-ink underline hover:opacity-80">/docs/security</a>.
            Violations may result in the rejection of your bundle, revocation of your plugin, or a ban of your
            publishing account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">5. No warranty</h2>
          <p>
            Plugins and themes on emdashcms.org are provided <strong class="text-ink font-medium">"as is"</strong>.
            We review every version with automated scans and, where budget allows, AI-assisted audits — but we do
            not execute plugins in sandboxed runtime environments and we cannot guarantee that any published plugin
            is safe, bug-free, or fit for purpose. Installing a plugin or theme is at your own risk.
          </p>
          <p>
            emdashcms.org, its operators, and its contributors are not liable for any damages arising from the use
            of plugins, themes, or the marketplace itself. If you need stronger guarantees, audit the source before
            installing — every bundle is downloadable and open.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">6. Reports and takedowns</h2>
          <p>
            Anyone can report a plugin or theme by clicking "Report a problem" on its detail page or visiting
            <code class="text-ink bg-paper-sunk px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono">{'/report/plugin/{id}'}</code>.
            We review reports promptly. For security issues, we may revoke the affected version immediately while
            the investigation proceeds.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">7. Changes to these terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these terms from time to time. Significant changes will be noted at the top of this page
            with a new "Last updated" date. Continued use of the marketplace after changes indicates acceptance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-ink mt-12 mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these terms? Open an issue on GitHub at
            <a href="https://github.com/chrisjohnleah/emdashcms-org/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ink underline hover:opacity-80">github.com/chrisjohnleah/emdashcms-org/issues</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="border-t border-rule pt-6 mt-10">
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-soft">
            The emdashcms.org marketplace code is MIT-licensed. Your use of the content on this site is governed
            by the original authors' licences (typically GPL, MIT, or Apache).
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
